column5: I just recently moved and was wondering if I have to change my boat registration/ownership address, I already did the trailer ownership. If so, can I do it online or do I have to go to the registration office.  Daniel
Thou shalt make yourself aware of the process and then you won't be wondering.    http://www.tc.gc.ca/eng/marinesafety/debs-obs-paperwork-paperwork_boat_licence-3212.htm#how3
